{"tid":2409604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬斯克邀普京Clubhouse對談 克宮：建議有趣","createTime":"2021-02-16T03:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T05:39:21.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a6cbce76c48cc755a059c3954445dd5ce4ad450a","tid":2409604,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-aOyxsAbRnLo/YCp8qx0oZ8I/AAAAAAAAH14/X0u4YIlhgqMTuHmCFhJlfAl_7AB7dL-CQCLcBGAsYHQ/s498/musktweet_210214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-aOyxsAbRnLo%2FYCp8qx0oZ8I%2FAAAAAAAAH14%2FX0u4YIlhgqMTuHmCFhJlfAl_7AB7dL-CQCLcBGAsYHQ%2Fs498%2Fmusktweet_210214.jpg&h=2c885305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國富豪馬斯克（Elon Musk）在美國時間星期六發出推特帖文，tag了克里姆林宮英文帳戶，用英語詢問：「你（俄羅斯總統普京）願意在Clubhouse一起對談嗎？」然後再用俄語補一句說，可以跟普京對談的話，他會很榮幸。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n克宮發言人今天（15日）回應了這個邀請，表示如果真的是邀請普京對談的話，這無疑是個很有趣的建議，但首先要弄清，那則帖文究竟意指什麼？真的是對談邀請的話，想談什麼？要搞清細節，才能正式回應。<br />\n<br />\n發言人又說，普京個人不使用社交媒體，沒有任何個人帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n不知道馬斯克為何想跟普京在Clubhouse對談。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克之前有時候也會在Twitter用俄語發推文。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克跟俄國最大的關係，是他的公司SpaceX。近年，送太空人及物資上太空，這項服務主要由俄羅斯提供，美國也要採用俄國的服務。SpaceX也推出這項服務後，便是俄國的市場對手，而且SpaceX的收費較俄國便宜，令沒了獨市生意的俄國要減價。<br />\n<br />\n在Twitter，馬斯克也不時跟俄國太空總署署長Dmitry Rogozin鬥嘴，後者曾批評SpaceX賤價搶客「做爛市」。<br />\n<br />\n在外國，由於有馬斯克等名人在Clubhouse的聊天室交談，因此流行起來。Clubhouse 近期在華文世界都成為話題，其中一個關於維吾爾族、藏族、漢族大陸人互相交流的聊天，最引人關注。 <br />\n<br />\nDW 早前有一篇文章，介紹較早前Clubhouse在德國流行的情況。<br />\n<br />\n近日，Clubhouse在大陸已被封鎖，需要用VPN才能前往。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/02/clubhouse.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2021%2F02%2Fclubhouse.html&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BnhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=4f0de7a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://europechinese.blogspot.com/2021/02/clubhouse.html</a>"},{"pid":"f33e80e53d5cae0dafb13206af3886bc654d04d7","tid":2409604,"uid":355289,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"做撚埋外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec76c10f2d60b19741a03f843b4f2ac95f3ca6a","tid":2409604,"uid":119232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"條友捧出嚟架空政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1763c563e0c68c6aeeda1fc4ac7f6c3e473c41","tid":2409604,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8169ffbca013567a2d53ebdfa6996e4c96b57690","tid":2409604,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:39:21.000Z","msg":"spaceX做俄佬生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}